OL,6,FWalking around the Central business
OL,7,Fdistrict there is a buzz on the
OL,8,Fstreets and its sleek silver
OL,9,Fskyscrapers look as iconic as ever,
OL,10,Fset against the green mountain peaks
OL,11,Fand hugging the water's edge.
OL,13,FBut to regular visitors, the city
OL,14,Ffeels and sounds different.
OL,16,FIn recent years, and again on this
OL,17,Fvisit, we noticed many more Chinese
OL,18,Fvisitors.
