OL,6,FBeijing has expanded a travel scheme
OL,7,Fallowing more mainland tourists and
OL,8,Ftour groups, so in the city centre
OL,9,FMandarin is commonly heard.
OL,11,FChinese is its official language,
OL,12,Falongside English, but the common
OL,13,Flanguage of Hong Kong is Cantonese.
OL,15,FOn Tuesday the waterfront was busy
OL,16,Fwith runners, tourists and locals
OL,17,Fenjoying the fine weather.
