OL,6,FNone of them appeared to be keeping an
OL,7,Feye on the marathon special
OL,8,Flegislative council meeting called to
OL,9,Fwrap up the debate on Article 23, the
OL,10,Fnew law that gives new powers to crack
OL,11,Fdown on any form of dissent.
OL,13,FWe'd arranged to meet with Dickson
OL,14,FChau from the League of Social
OL,15,FDemocrats.
OL,17,FThey are one of the few pro-democratic
OL,18,Fgroups still operating in the city and
OL,19,Feven dared to stage a when Article 23
OL,20,Fbegan its first reading.
