OL,6,FA far cry from the half a million
OL,7,Fpeople who took to the streets in 2003
OL,8,Fwhen the bill was first proposed and
OL,9,Fultimately shelved due to the strength
OL,10,Fof public opposition.
OL,12,FDickson was nervous about the location
OL,13,Fon the waterfront, close to the
OL,14,FLegislative Council headquarters, and
OL,15,Fas we were talking he could see some
OL,16,Fplain-clothed officers gathering in
OL,17,Fthe background.
OL,19,FThey didn't intervene until the end of
OL,20,Four interview, when they approached
OL,21,FDickson.
