OL,6,FThey didn't ask his name but addressed
OL,7,Fhim as "Mr Chau" and asked him what he
OL,8,Fwas doing and when he'd be finished.
OL,10,FWe've become used to seeing this kind
OL,11,Fof interaction in China, but it's new
OL,12,Fin Hong Kong.
OL,14,FAlthough Dickson spoke to us honestly,
OL,15,FI could tell that he was watching what
OL,16,Fhe said, careful not to go too far in
OL,17,Fhis criticism of Article 23 or the
OL,18,Floss of free and open discourse in
OL,19,FHong Kong.
