OL,6,FHe admitted that the risks are getting
OL,7,Fhigher, and it is no longer safe for
OL,8,Fpeople to express their views on
OL,9,Fpolitical matters because there might
OL,10,Fbe consequences for your job, your
OL,11,Fstudies or your future.
OL,13,FWhen we tried to talk to people on the
OL,14,Fstreet to gauge knowledge and opinions
OL,15,Fon Article 23, we struggled to get
OL,16,Fanyone to speak.
