OL,6,F''Better not'' was the common response
OL,7,Fand we came across one man who was
OL,8,Fonly in the city to visit his parents
OL,9,F` he'd moved to England two years ago
OL,10,Fdue to the political climate.
OL,12,FWe agreed that the city felt like a
OL,13,Fchanged place. One woman did tell us
OL,14,Fthat she felt it was good for the city
OL,15,Fto be peaceful again.
OL,17,FI've been based in Beijing for eight
OL,18,Fyears and reported several times over
OL,19,Fthose years, almost monthly during the
OL,20,F2019 protests.
