OL,6,FWe have covered Xi Jinping's visits
OL,7,Fand handover anniversaries and it used
OL,8,Fto be somewhere we could come to talk
OL,9,Fto NGOs who were unable to .
OL,11,FNow most of those NGOs have left Hong
OL,12,FKong too.
OL,14,FThe introduction of Article 23 is
OL,15,Fworrying local journalists, who have
OL,16,Fseen their operating environment
OL,17,Fgreatly restricted and who were
OL,18,Falready poring over every word they
OL,19,Fwrote fearing the national security
OL,20,Flaw imposed by .
