OL,4,Cpossibly forever
OL,6,FThere is now a whole new set of
OL,7,Fregulations regarding state secrets,
OL,8,Ftreason, insurrection, and sabotage
OL,9,Ffor them to navigate.
OL,11,FOne of the new offences contained in
OL,12,FArticle 23 relates to the unlawful use
OL,13,Fof a computer or electronic system to
OL,14,Fendanger national security. It is
OL,15,Fpunishable by 20 years in jail.
OL,17,FLike many sections of the bill the
OL,18,Fterms are extremely broad and
OL,19,Fintentionally vague.
