OL,6,FThe pro-democracy supporters who we
OL,7,Fhave still been able to talk to in
OL,8,FHong Kong remain hopeful that the tide
OL,9,Fwill change.
OL,11,FDickson talked about keeping the
OL,12,FLeague of Social Democrats running for
OL,13,Fthe sake of his colleagues who have
OL,14,Fbeen imprisoned. Most for their roles .
OL,16,FHong Kong Chief Executive John Lee
OL,17,Fdescribed the passing of Article 23 as
OL,18,Fan historic moment, and told the
OL,19,Flegislative council that they had
OL,20,Faccomplished an honourable mission
OL,21,Ftogether.
